{"tid":2192784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我用程式狙擊五毛，結果比人ban三日 (2)","createTime":"2020-09-07T10:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T10:55:55.000Z","uid":62025,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"175edb0b32c636879a6e2513aea7cb2c3f9397f7","tid":2192784,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>幫樓豬開POST2 個POST/BOT都唔係我既</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我之前一直有個bot，只要我狙擊對象一開post，個bot就會自動留言，如下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymcPr9Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymcPr9Y.png&h=38f0e2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點先會成為狙擊目標呢？<br />\n<br />\n每見到一次五毛發言，我都會mark入database<br />\n<br />\n當database入面同一個會員有超過5次五毛言論紀錄，機械人就會開始狙擊<br />\n<br />\n結果係點呢？<br />\n<br />\n結果班五毛同PR群起report我<br />\n<br />\n係7月20號，admin以「惡意洗板」為理由ban狙我三日<br />\n<br />\n更加話如有再犯就ban更耐，甚至永ban<br />\n<br />\n咁我由7月20號開始send過幾封email比admin，提出上訴啦<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">截至今日，我未收到admin，任何回覆</span><br />\n<br />\n你個email冇人睇既就唔好撚擺出黎啦<br />\n<br />\n不過算啦你連自己個連登都未必睇，點會睇email<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家真係要聽Brian Cha講「唔中意？Quit狙佢囉」<br />\n<br />\n令人唔想上連登之 - 垃圾留言精選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f1ed67a3560f14a7f2e32e7573929e9150a5f7e6","tid":2192784,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"推 預計呢個POST大量五毛入黎負評<br />\nQUOTE番我上個POST既留言:-<br />\n成堆五毛喺到針住夠唔夠客觀同言論自由<br />\n屌你老母入去個POST睇下樓主cap出黎既例子 如果有邊個唔啱既咪拎出黎討論下順便幫佢平反囉<br />\n再唔係既話, 你拎個樓主狙擊錯誤既例子俾我睇下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令人唔想上連登之 - 垃圾留言精選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192085</a>"},{"pid":"3aa51c6447e6d8bf988b21b4a4b73c4647a2a85a","tid":2192784,"uid":126782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"對樓豬來講 全世界都係五毛<br />\n<br />\n殊不知自己用boot先係最影響討論區生態<br />\n<br />\n被ban只係啱啱好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5e982932f4f9f04b97c7c51a03f1e49c7bcd07","tid":2192784,"uid":58089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aa51c6447e6d8bf988b21b4a4b73c4647a2a85a","tid":2192784,"uid":126782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"對樓豬來講 全世界都係五毛<br />\n<br />\n殊不知自己用boot先係最影響討論區生態<br />\n<br />\n被ban只係啱啱好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"係咁洗版阻鳩住哂 仲聲大大咁屌返人轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076dec407c9f905989007a97995d6208ad8689f6","tid":2192784,"uid":290025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea5e982932f4f9f04b97c7c51a03f1e49c7bcd07","tid":2192784,"uid":58089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aa51c6447e6d8bf988b21b4a4b73c4647a2a85a","tid":2192784,"uid":126782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"對樓豬來講 全世界都係五毛<br />\n<br />\n殊不知自己用boot先係最影響討論區生態<br />\n<br />\n被ban只係啱啱好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"係咁洗版阻鳩住哂 仲聲大大咁屌返人轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"先唔講個BOT有冇影響,連登咁多巴打,點解會比樓主一言堂決定邊個係5毛邊個唔係?權力過大了"}]}